ls, and jaundice.', 'Synergism', 'Golimumab, Ustekinumab, Antithymocyte immunoglobulin (rabbit), Secukinumab, Canakinumab, Ravulizumab, Mycophenolic acid, Tacrolimus, Abatacept, Upadacitinib, Anakinra, More', 'Oprelvekin, Elapegademase, Sargramostim, Histamine, Pegademase, Pegfilgrastim, Filgrastim, Glatiramer', 'Moderate', NULL, 'DDInter', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/87240/', '[1] "Product Information. Plegridy (peginterferon beta-1a)." Biogen Idec Inc, Cambridge, MA.[2] "Product Information. Betaseron (interferon beta-1b)." Berlex, Richmond, CA.[3] "Product Information. Rebif (interferon beta-1a)." Serono Laboratories Inc, Norwell, MA.[4] "Product Information. Avonex (interferon beta-1a)." Biogen, Cambridge, MA.', 1767369485);
